{"tid":2427147,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"超大質量黑洞也許非來自物質吸積，而是暗物質暈直接塌縮","createTime":"2021-02-28T14:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T17:11:44.000Z","uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e636def601719719cca08b45b5233e71aa709da8","tid":2427147,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T14:48:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HhY8OVl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHhY8OVl.jpg&h=66d1149d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早期宇宙出現超大質量黑洞的事實至今仍令科學家迷惑，究竟哪裡來的時間讓它們吸收大<br />\n量物質？最近又有研究指出，超大質量黑洞的形成可能不是來自緩慢吸積過程，而是星系<br />\n中心高密度區域的暗物質。<br />\n <br />\n在當今星系演化中，一個最大問題就是早期宇宙形成超大質量黑洞的確切方式，根據標準<br />\n理論，黑洞透過不斷吸收重子物質（組成恆星、行星和所有可見物體的原子和元素）來增<br />\n長，這是一段漫長過程，照理說不太可能在早期宇宙出現超大質量黑洞，但我們卻在大爆<br />\n炸後 8 億年內就觀察到超大質量黑洞，科學家對於它們如何迅速發展至這尺寸尚不清楚<br />\n。<br />\n <br />\n來自拉普拉塔大學（IGFAE）天文學家 Carlos Arguelles 領導的團隊，於是決定往暗物<br />\n質暈方向研究。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://phys.org/news/2021-02-supermassive-black-holes-dark.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphys.org%2Fnews%2F2021-02-supermassive-black-holes-dark.html&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3YgDU6S0x1vJ5b5MQMl6fZo%3D&h=213c3302\" target=\"_blank\">https://phys.org/news/2021-02-supermassive-black-holes-dark.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2021/02/28/supermassive-black-hole-dark-matter/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2021%2F02%2F28%2Fsupermassive-black-hole-dark-matter%2F&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3YgDU6S0x1vJ5b5MQMl6fZo%3D&h=1b1b4e3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2021/02/28/supermassive-black-hole-dark-matter/</a>"},{"pid":"965c279c016a6b3cae61204e2dad713c8d6f6ff3","tid":2427147,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T14:51:46.000Z","msg":"「大爆炸後 8 億年內就觀察到超大質量黑洞」係你地推算出嚟嘅<br />\n<br />\n暗物質你地又證實唔到嘅<br />\n<br />\n講經咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid